#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_short_boxed: Black"
msgstr "5-短絡腮鬍：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_short_boxed: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid ""
"You have a black moustache and a short beard with trimmed sides.  Thin "
"patches connect them both, forming a 'box' around the lips, thus the name."
msgstr "你有一撮黑色的小鬍子和兩側修剪整齊的短絡腮鬍。稀疏的毛髮將兩者連接起來，在嘴唇周圍形成一個“方框”，因此得名。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_goatee: Black"
msgstr "5-山羊鬍：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_goatee: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "You have a short black beard at the tip of your chin."
msgstr "你的下巴尖上有一撮黑色的短山羊鬍。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_full: Black"
msgstr "5-全臉胡：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_full: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid ""
"You have a black moustache and a long beard, both formed by allowing free "
"growth of hair, with no particular styling."
msgstr "你有一撮黑色的小鬍子和長長的絡腮鬍，兩者都是任由毛髮自由生長而成，沒有特別的造型。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_chevron: Black"
msgstr "5-八字鬍：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_chevron: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "You have a black moustache that covers your entire top lip."
msgstr "你有一撮覆蓋整個上唇的黑色八字鬍。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_neckbeard: Black"
msgstr "5-頸須：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_neckbeard: Black'}
#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid ""
"You have a black beard formed from hair grown on neck below the chin line.  "
"No moustache included."
msgstr "你有一撮由下巴線以下頸部生長的毛髮形成的黑色頸須。不包括小鬍子。"

#: .\changes\1_add_beard.json
msgid "5-beard_moustache: Black"
msgstr "5-鬍鬚_小鬍子：黑色"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '5-beard_moustache: Black'}
